result.name: Thai E-San Ram Mis

reviews.text: Decent Thai restaurant in Kowloon City, which is home of many Thai places.  Food here is not especially remarkable, the main point of this place is it's opening hours.  It closes at 6am in the morning so it is perfect for those late night Thai cravings, when not much else is open.
Food is very good here and good for a late dinner
